ed to provide annotation-related information","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"to a map view. To use this protocol, you adopt it in any custom objects that","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"store or represent annotation data. Each object then serves as the source of","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"information about a single map annotation and provides critical information,","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"such as the annotation’s location on the map. Annotation objects do not provide","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"the visual representation of the annotation but typically coordinate (in","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"conjunction with the map view’s delegate) the creation of an appropriate","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"objects to handle the display.","type":"text"}],"kind":"symbol","role":"symbol","type":"topic"},"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre/MLNMapSnapshotter/addAnnotations:":{"type":"topic","fragments":[{"kind":"text","text":"- "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"addAnnotations:"}],"navigatorTitle":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"addAnnotations:"}],"url":"\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnmapsnapshotter\/addannotations:","role":"symbol","kind":"symbol","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"Adds an array of annotations to the snapshotter."}],"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNMapSnapshotter\/addAnnotations:","title":"addAnnotations:"},"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre/MLNMultiPoint":{"kind":"symbol","fragments":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"MLNMultiPoint"}],"abstract":[{"text":"The ","type":"text"},{"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNMultiPoint","isActive":true,"type":"reference"},{"text":" class is an abstract superclass used to define shapes","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"composed of multiple vertices.","type":"tex